(104, 1, 'A basic guide to help your travel agency grow.', 'a-basic-guide-to-help-your-travel-agency-grow', '<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\">One of the basic aims of almost every other travel agency is to increase the volume of sales and capture and attract new clients to their business. What travel agencies tend to forget is the constantly increasing levels of business in the industry. With such high levels of business, it can sometimes be hard for you to expand as an organization and you also may end up taking the wrong steps to make your organization grow. It is extremely unfortunate for a travel agency to end up losing focus of who they are in an attempt to expand an organization. This article provides some helpful tips that can be used by travel agencies to stay in focus.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\">First and foremost, it is extremely important to make sure that the spotlight is on your travel agency as compared to it being on your competitors. To do that, you should highlight the benefits that your clients will gain if they choose to avail of the services being provided by you as compared to your competitors. A good way of doing that could be by highlighting and pointing out your strengths to your target market rather than focusing on dealing with the ever-growing competition. You can also ask some of your loyal customers to review the services they availed from your travel agency and to post them on their social media accounts along with mentioning the name of your organization. This could help you to attract more potential customers.</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\">It is important to make your customers feel as if they are being heard and you acknowledge the fact that they have chosen your travel agency as compared to your competitors. To do that, you must interact with your customers and make sure that you develop a healthy relationship with them. We are currently living in the world in which having a presence on social media is considered to be important so different social media platforms, for example, Instagram and Facebook can be used to have interactive sessions with your customers. This will show your potential clients that your organization realizes what the customers want and are striving towards fulfilling that demand.</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\">Instead of just trying to sell the services that you offer, your organization should aim towards providing a joyful experience that stays in the memory of your clients. Instead of just fulfilling what your customer demands from you, a better idea would be to also make different recommendations according to the nature of your customer and their preferences. For example, if a customer is into adventure, then you can recommend some of the unique destinations where they could fulfill their need of doing something adventurous and something fun. Not only will this satisfy your customer, but it will also be helpful for you to generate more revenues that way.</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\">Instead of offering individual services, you can come up with different and interesting packages for your clients. For example, if your client wants you to make reservations and booking for them, instead of just doing what you can come up with a unique package that involves multiple services such as other activities along with the hotel reservations and the flight bookings. This way your client will get to avail a lot more of your services and they will feel as if they are getting more out of what they are being charged for, in easy words, they will feel as if they are saving money by availing services from you rather than availing them from other travel agencies that are competing against you.</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\">Another important factor that it is taken into consideration can help your business grow is by finding a niche market. Finding a niche market for your organization to target does not necessarily mean that you are targeting a small group of people, it means that the services that you are offering to your target market are very unique as compared to your competition. This will not only set you apart but it will also help you to develop more customer loyalty. </span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\">These days, time is money and one can not simply waste their time on small tasks such as finding out the levels of inventory in different hotels or searching for the different routes that flights might take. As an organization, you should purchase software that helps you with these tasks and saves you time. Purchasing software can initially sound a little intimidating as they are expensive if the correct software is chosen for your organization to perform specific tasks then it can help in growing your organization. It will also give you an edge over your competitors in the market as your organization will be more technologically advanced as compared to them.</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\">Developing a healthy and long-term relationship with your clients is the key to instilling the element of trust in them. Once a client feels that your organization is trustworthy, that particular client will automatically be comfortable with the decisions that you take for them. For example, if a client is satisfied with your organization and begins to trust you, he will let you plan their trip for them and all that is left for them to do is pay you. Another benefit of creating long term relationships with your clients is that they will start to feel that whatever you charge from them will be justified as they have never had any bad past experiences with your organization. This will also help your travel agency to create loyal customers which will indirectly lead your travel agency to grow.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '', 1, 1, 0, 'image_750x_5f86fc5c32c3e.jpg', 828, '2020-10-14 16:27:12'),
(105, 1, 'Tips to increase revenues and reduce costs of a travel agency', 'tips-to-increase-revenues-and-reduce-costs-of-a-travel-agency', '<p>Nowadays, travel is a part of almost every person&#39;s life. People love traveling with their family, friends and loved one and not only regular people, but traveling is also required in multiple different fields as well. According to a study, the travel industry is the 5th most expensive industry globally. Not only are the costs high for the travel agents but the costs incurred by the customers and the prices that they have to pay are also not that low. This article highlights some of the ways and some of the tactics that can be implemented in a travel agency to cut their costs and increase the levels of revenues being generated.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p><strong>First and foremost, </strong>you should have access to different hotel and airline inventories. The reason why it is so important to be well aware of all the hotel and flight inventories is that you will know the prices that are being offered by those specific hotels and airlines. Hotel reservations and flight bookings are the most expensive part of traveling, especially the flight bookings, so having access to the inventories and being well informed about the prices means that you have the option to choose from them and offer what is best for your customers. Airlines usually tend to save up the VIP prices for their corporate clients and these prices are not generally available to the public. Having access to those prices and rates means that the travel agency has the power of negotiation in its hands which means lesser prices for the final customer and more profits for the travel agency.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p><strong>Another important factor </strong>that needs to be taken into consideration is all the planning that goes into the final trip by the travel agency. Whether it is a leisure trip being planned by a group of friends or a business trip being planned by someone who belongs to the corporate sector, it is important to do pre-plan everything ahead of time. This will help you cut up the probable costs that you may have to incur as a travel agent since you will be ruling out all the possibilities of any negative circumstances taking place during the trip of your client. For example, making sure that the hotel rooms are up to the standards of your clients so that they are not disappointed when they reach their hotel. In case the hotel rooms are not up to the standards of your client, the client will ask you to book another hotel room for them whose cost will be incurred by you.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>It is extremely important to inform your customers if their budget is in alignment with all the services that they plan to enjoy during their trip. For example, small things like transportation and wifi facilities may not be accounted for in the beginning but these are those small things that might add up to your total cost at the end of the day. Since the cost will increase, there will be a good chance that it will result in the budget provided by the client not being enough and hence a dissatisfied client at the end of the day. Another reason why it is important to make sure that your client is well aware of all of these expenses is that you, as a travel agency, do not have to incur these costs on the behalf of the customer, in case they were not accounted for beforehand. If that happens, it can greatly add up to your costs and your expenses and the customer will not be held accountable to pay for these expenses as they were not informed about them by you in the first place.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>These days, organizations are more focused on generated more revenues and earning profits but while the organizations are busy doing that, they tend to ignore the main resource that they have which is their employees. Keeping the motivation levels high of your employees is extremely important as they are the main reason why your organization is under operating conditions. Having demotivated employees mean that your costs are automatically going up without you doing much about it. The reason for that is that is your employees are not working up to the standards that you have set for them, they may not efficiently provide the best services to your clients. This automatically means that your customers will be dissatisfied and they may not return to you which is a negative consequence of decreased levels of customer loyalty. All of this will eventually lead to lesser revenues being generated by your travel agency hence lesser profits and higher costs. To avoid your costs being raised because of demotivated employees, it is important to come up with different ways to keep them giving their best performance.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>If all of these measures are taken and all of these factors are taken into consideration, your travel agency is bound to generate more revenues hence more profits and decrease the costs that are being incurred along with reducing the risk of the costs increasing in the long run, which will lead your<strong><a href=\"https://www.phptravels.com\"> travel agency</a></strong> to bloom and grow.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'Tips to increase revenues and reduce costs of a travel agency, how increase the revenue of a travel agency in 2020, Tips to increase revenues and reduce costs of a travel agency in 2020', 1, 1, 0, 'image_750x_5f3e628bf2a08.jpg', 845, '2020-08-20 16:27:42'),
(106, 1, 'Common mistakes that can make your travel agency suffer and different ways to avoid them', 'common-mistakes-that-can-make-your-travel-agency-suffer-and-different-ways-to-avoid-them', '<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\">With the constant developments being observed day by day, the number of factors disrupting the daily business activities of travel agencies is also increasing day by day. There are several factors that travel agencies, or any other business organization, might have to consider even before taking the tiniest of decisions. For example, if a travel agency decides to come up with a new service that they plan on offering their clients, they might have to consider factors like their budget, to what extent will that new service impact their revenues and the services being offered by their competitors. During the process of considering these factors, travel agencies might end up making a few incorrect decisions or mistakes that can have a massive negative impact on the organization as a whole. However, there are ways to fix the mistakes that have already been made or ways to avoid them altogether.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\">One of the most basic and the most common mistake that is made by travel agencies is the lack of personalization that is being offered. People appreciate it when an organization remembers their past purchases and keeps a record or their information, it makes the client feel as if the organization is concerned about their likes and dislikes. Lack of personalization can make it harder for your clients to decide for themselves. For example, there are times when the client themselves are not sure about what they want or what they require, that is when they start to rely on the travel agency to help them out and tell them what is best for them or what is in their interest. Sometimes customers also feel overwhelmed when they see a lot of information being provided on a website of the preferred travel agency because that makes them even more indecisive about their options. A very good and easy way to solve this problem would be to employ a system that helps you keep track of everything related to your previous clients. That way, the customer will also feel hiring your travel agency and they won&rsquo;t consider the other competitive agencies in the market. This will also increase the level of customer loyalty, indirectly.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\">The second mistake that is usually made by travel agencies is not offering extended or more complex services to their clients. These days, when a client hires a travel agent or decides to employ a travel agency, they expect the travel agency to take care of every little detail. Clients expect that the travel agency provides them with all the extended services along with the basic ones that are provided by all the other travel agencies. For example, along with making the bookings and the reservations, planning out tours or helping out your client with the visa formalities can be the extended services that your travel agency can offer. Your travel agency can also offer customized packages and discounts according to the preferences and the requirements of your clients.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\">Travel agencies need to understand and should be able to differentiate business trips and leisure trips. Clients planning a business trip have different demands and requirements as compared to clients who are looking forward to planning a leisure trip. If the travel agencies can do that efficiently, they will be able to save a lot of their time and the travelers&rsquo; money. One of the most prominent differences between a business trip and a leisure trip is the flexibility of dates. On a business trip, the travel agent can not play around with the dates. Price is another factor that can help a travel agency determine the difference. On a business trip, lower prices are not the topmost priority since the top priority of the client is getting things done in an orderly manner. Clients planning a business trip may ask for facilities like a stable wifi connection of a hotel reservation that is closer to the workplace whereas a client planning a leisure trip may inquire about different restaurants or tourist destinations. Knowing what your client wants can be extremely beneficial for both the client and the travel agency as it will save time, money and help the travel agency to understand the demand of its customers better.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\">Information overload is another mistake that is usually made by travel agencies. A perception has been created that the more information that you provide for your current and potential client to explore, the better it is. This is not always true because you might think that you are indirectly helping out your client but you might end up overwhelming them with all the information that has been uploaded on your website. People usually prefer to get informed about the things that are relevant and helpful only to them, providing a lot of information that is of no use to the client might confuse them. A study conducted showed that 60 percent of the potential clients of an online travel agency leave the website as the information overload confuses them about the decisions they wanted to make. A lot of information may even lead to the ineffectiveness of the relevant information that has been provided. To avoid this problem, your website should be divided into different parts or sections that provide specific information. That way, if a client wants to know about something, they can visit that particular section of your website.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\">Not having a personal blog is another mistake that is usually made by travel agencies. Having a blog may make your clients feel as if they are getting an opportunity to know more about your travel agency on a personal level. This is a great way to develop a healthy and long-term relationship with your client as they will feel as they can trust your organization and the decision it makes for that particular client. The blog created for your travel agency can have different pictorial articles of a wide variety of different topics, for example, the role played by social media in our lives or the benefits of working with an online travel agency.</span></p>\r\n', '', 1, 1, 0, 'image_750x_5e8c7d0e703ef.jpg', 1423, '2020-04-07 16:28:14'),
(107, 1, 'Traveling independently or hiring a travel agency – which one is better.', 'traveling-independently-or-hiring-a-travel-agency-which-one-is-better', '<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\">With all the information provided through different sources, the options available for people to choose from are endless. Travelling has been made easier because of all these options available but at the same time, it has become more difficult because all the information available can sometimes confuse and overwhelm the traveler. This article will highlight the pros and cons that revolve around hiring a travel agency and will identify the difference in the experience that a traveler may experience in both ways.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\">Let us start by talking a little about the travel agencies and what their basic role in our lives is. As a traveler, hiring a travel agency would automatically make your life easier. All you have to do is tell them your requirements and provide them will all the information required to plan your trip, pay them and think about enjoying your trip. Hiring a travel agency would mean that everything related to your trip or vacation is being taken care of. From fulfilling all the formalities of visa application to flight bookings and hotel reservations, everything is taken care of by a travel agency that you have chosen to hire. In a shorter sentence, hiring a travel agency is more like a one-stop-shop where you can avail and enjoy all the services that you demand or require. Not only will choosing the correct travel agency help in saving a lot of hassle that the traveler might have to go through, but it will also help the traveler to save a lot of time and not. It will also help the travel agency to generate more business. These days, all the good travel agencies have bought different software that can help them meet the demands and requirements of the customers that can help the travel agency make all the decisions on the clients&rsquo; behalf. A big benefit to travelers in hiring a travel agency is that they can avail of many different discounts and offers and save even more money.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\">With the wide variety of travel agencies available from which a traveler can choose from, some people still prefer to travel independently as they feel that they are more comfortable when they are on their own or when they are not associated with any travel agency. Traveling independently means that you get to make all the major decisions yourself and not only the major decisions but also the smaller day to day decisions that you might have to make when you are traveling. A study conducted showed that by traveling independently, a person can spend their entire day with less than 25 dollars of expense. Some people also have the perception that by traveling independently, they will be able to save up a lot of money as they would not have to pay for the services that they might have availed if they hired a travel agency to do all the work for them. Not only does the traveler has to pay for the services but a part of the costs of the organization and a part of the profit margin of the organization is also borne by the traveler. Another advantage that travelers seem to enjoy when traveling independently is that they are not restricted to a particular routine or a schedule that has been designed for them. They get to eat, sleep, and go wherever they want whenever they want. However, this can also be a disadvantage because a person naturally needs some form of guidance when they are traveling alone on foreign land.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\">When a traveler decides to hire a travel agency, choosing the correct travel agency that fits your needs and requirements is the first and the most important step that needs to be taken extremely cautiously. First and foremost, you need to finalize and list down all of your needs and requirements that you expect the travel agency to fulfill. After you have shortlisted all of your needs, requirements, expectations and most importantly your budget, that is when you start searching for an appropriate travel agency.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\">In today&#39;s world, research can be done through multiple different mediums but the best and the fastest way is to Google the most suitable travel agency. Once the traveler feels that the correct travel agency has been found, that is the time when the traveler should reach out to the travel agency, talk to the agent and try to negotiate the price and work upon the rest of the requirements. This is also the time when the travel agency can identify and educate the traveler about how they function and what to expect from them. Most travel agencies are in association with different organizations or institutions, for example, hotels and airlines, in different countries. Once the traveler has provided the travel agency with all the relevant information that is required, the travel agency starts to plan and organize the trip for the traveler to enjoy. When it comes to the travel agency to provide the services that they have promised or the services that have been demanded by the traveler, it is important that there is an effective and efficient communication network between the travel agency and the traveler themselves. That is because it is important to provide the traveler with constant updates as to how much work has been done. Not only an efficient communication network is important between the traveler and the travel agency but it is also essential to have an efficient and effective communication network between the travel agency and the different organizations globally. This is important because the travel agency will be aware and will have access to the inventories of different organizations, for example, hotels and airlines, and can make reservations for the traveler accordingly.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\">Traveling independently is always an option for everyone. As long as you have done an ample amount of research that is related to your desired trip and if you are confident enough to deal with any possible inconveniences or handle and organize the entire trip on your own, then traveling independently should not be a big problem for you. However, hiring a travel agent also has its&rsquo; advantages as mentioned above and it is always the best and the safest option one can go for.</span></p>\r\n', 'Traveling independently , hiring a travel agency, travel industry', 1, 1, 0, 'image_750x_5e898f3977d24.jpg', 1158, '2020-04-05 16:28:34'),
(108, 1, 'Successful ways to advertise your travel agency', 'successful-ways-to-advertise-your-travel-agency', '<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\">Developing an organization is not the easiest thing in the world, but once your organization has been developed, it would not be of many benefits to you unless you try to put it out there in the market. Establishing a business can be stressful putting advertising and marketing your business correctly is even more important. This is the same as all businesses, even travel agencies. Unless people know about your organization or what you are offering, you will not be able to gain any benefits from all the effort you initially put in to establish your business.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\">Traveling independently is not easy at all, in fact, it can really stress people out, so the demand for travel agencies is still high. But with the high levels of competition in different markets, it is important to put in extra effort in order to beat your competitors. As people try to avoid as much hassle as they could, they prefer to hire a travel agency to plan and organize their trips for them but letting your potential clients know that your organization exists is the key to generating more clients.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\">First and foremost, it is extremely important to come up with a basic strategy that will be implemented throughout your travel agency in order to effectively advertise. A strategy consists of two main parts, the plan, and the objectives. The objectives include the long-term and the short-term goals of your organization that need to be met and a plan is a way to meet those objectives that have been met. In the case of advertising, the main objective would be to put your organization out there in the market and generate more clients. If we classify this even further, the short-term plan could attract more clients and the long-term objective could be increasing the number of revenues being generated through those clients and the level of business growth.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\">Once these particular objectives have been set and highlighted, a plan helps the organization to achieve those objectives in a particular time frame. In the plan, the current situation of advertising should also be highlighted. For example, the current modes of advertising that the travel agency is implementing and how effective they have proven to be. A travel agency should never solely rely on a specific medium of advertising for long periods of time. For example, if a travel agency has been advertising its services through social media or text messages for a very long period of time, the advertisement might end up being ineffective after some time. It is better to keep switching between different mediums of advertising in order to capture and retain the attention of your target audience.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\">Another way of effective advertising can be through creative online advertisements for your travel agency. You can create pages on different social media platforms such as Instagram or Facebook in order to increase the level of viewership. These days, almost every other person has a phone with Facebook or Instagram installed in it so it will be extremely easy to capture the attention of people through these social media platforms. Different codes and special discounts can also be offered to those people to approach your travel agency through those pages on social media. This way, more people will feel inclined towards viewing your page as they will be interested in availing different offers and discounts. A big advantage of using these social media platforms is that you can be as creative as you want you. You have the option of using different pictorial images and videos. People usually feel inclined towards colorful images and videos which will help you to attract new clients.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\">Different bloggers and influencers can also be approached and paid in order to help you advertise your travel agency. People tend to trust bloggers and social media influencers as they feel that they can relate to these bloggers and influencers on a personal level so hiring them to advertise your travel agency can prove to be beneficial for you. One thing that you need to keep in mind before deciding on which social media platform you want to use is how much viewership you expected to gain from that platform. A study conducted stated that 86 percent of the travel agencies use Facebook as they find advertising their organization through Facebook to be more effective. This decision also depends on the demographics of your target audience.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\">A potential client is most likely to have a look at your social media accounts, but they will most definitely visit the official website of your travel agency in order to gain more information regarding what you have to offer. It is important to keep the overall look and the design of your website colorful and attractive. If the website of your travel agency is dull, it will probably bore your potential client which will result in them looking for other travel agencies whom they find to be more attractive, who are also your competitors. It is important to keep your website informative but providing too much information can result in an information overload. When an information overload occurs, the viewer is unable to retain high levels of information being provided and hence all the efforts of designing your website go to waste.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\">Another thing that is extremely important is to design your website in such a way that it is interactive and that your current or potential clients can have all of their questions and queries addressed. Another important factor that needs to be considering before designing your website is that your website should be designed in such a way that it can also be used by people through mobile phones without having to go through a lot of hassle. A study conducted showed that almost 50 percent of the people visit different websites through their mobile phones so if your website is not optimized for people using mobile phones then you might end up losing that 50 percent, which is a massive chunk of your revenues, to your competitors.</span></p>\r\n', 'successful advertisement,  best ways to market, good marketing strategy, successful marketing ways', 1, 1, 0, 'image_750x_5e82f95c4f600.jpg', 1125, '2020-03-31 16:29:09'),
(109, 1, 'How to get global hotels inventory and sell online', 'how-to-get-global-hotels-inventory-and-sell-online', '<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\">The inventories of any hotel are considered to be its biggest asset. It shows the amount of investment that has been done and indirectly, it also shows how expanded and well established that particular chain of hotels is. Managing the inventory of your hotel is a very big task for a hotelier because you need to make sure how much inventory is tied up and how much of it is occupied. You need to stay updated about the levels of hotel inventory at all times to manage your Consumer demand accordingly. Efficiently managing the hotel inventory can prove to be extremely beneficial for your hotel in the long run. For example, Marriott increased its annual revenues by 200 million dollars when they introduced inventory management systems.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\">Inventory management is a very broad term that includes the management of a hotels&rsquo; room inventory. It includes understanding and controlling the inventories in such a way that it not only generates but also increases the consumer demand and hence the revenues. Analyzing and keeping a constant check on your inventory is important because it also helps you to determine the seasons in which you get the maximum demand and the seasons in which you get the lowest demand. That way, it makes it easier for you to manage the high demand season and helps you to generate more demand in the trough seasons. The concept of dynamic pricing can also be implemented to generate demand in the trough seasons. Dynamic pricing is a strategy in which your prices change according to the demand being generated. Inventory management also helps the hotel to be aware of the prices being offered by the competitors and helps the online travel agencies to choose from the hotels available depending on the level of transparency of the prices being offered.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\">The hotels need to come up with different balanced strategies that can help them track and promote their hotel inventories to the travel agencies. If the inventories are not managed properly, it can create a lot of financial problems for the hotel itself along with the travel agency. Technology has played a major role in helping the hotels and the travel agencies to keep a track of the inventories and hence manage the demand that is being generated. If the travel agencies as updated with the inventories, they will be able to book the best hotel suited to their client. One of the ways through which the advanced observed in technology has helped the travel agencies to have access to and keep track of the hotel inventories if through knowing the lead time. To maximize the number of revenues being generated by a travel agency, you need to know the time it will take to sell the hotel rooms. Travel agencies can then accordingly, know how much access they require to the inventories of different hotels.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\">Another important factor that online travel agencies need to consider is the level of distribution. This means that the travel agencies need to know the minimum amount of hotel bookings that they need to make to maintain their revenues or how much more hotel bookings are required which will help them to increase their revenues. Different booking engines can also be used that can greatly help the travel agencies to keep track of the distribution of the different hotel inventories. If we think about the distribution of hotel inventories in this aspect, the travel agencies need to keep track of the inventories so that they can manage their bookings accordingly. Travel agencies also need to keep track and constantly monitor the sales and the demand of the hotel inventories to effectively promote, maintain and manage the levels of inventories. Different software can be used to help the travel agencies to take care of the inventories.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\">Having the correct type of technology within your organization is extremely important for the travel agencies to have access to hotel inventories and sell them online because this is something that can not happen if your travel agency is not in alignment with the other departments within the organization, for example, the marketing team, the finance team, and the team responsible for the sales management. There is a big variety of different software in the market that have been developed in the last few numbers of years that can help your travel agency to understand the different organizational departments a little better and help you stay in alignment with them. If your travel agency purchases any of the software available in the market, your travel agency will have all the information that is required from within the organization and multiple decisions can be made simultaneously without wasting much time. Purchasing software may sound a little intimidating at first or even maybe a waste of money but if your travel agency purchases the correct software, it can prove to be extremely beneficial for your travel agency in the long run.</span></p>\r\n', 'hotels inventory, global hotels rooms, hotels rooms inventory, sell hotels online', 1, 1, 0, 'image_750x_5e6f89c6e2076.jpg', 1140, '2020-03-16 16:29:35'),
(110, 1, 'Some of the very basic marketing mistakes that are usually made by travel agencies', 'some-of-the-very-basic-marketing-mistakes-that-are-usually-made-by-travel-agencies', '<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\">You can invest endlessly in your business but if you do not market it well enough, you won&rsquo;t be gaining much from what you have already invested. In general, terms, marketing your business means putting your business out there and letting people know what you have in store to offer. Marketing is extremely important because it creates a perception about the product or service that you are offering in the minds of your client, for example, if you want to create a perception or an image that you are offering high-end products or services then you will market your brand accordingly. Businesses sometimes tend to lose focus and they stop concentrating on marketing their organization once they have established themselves. This is when people in organizations start to make big mistakes that are related to marketing that can eventually be harmful for their organization in the long run and the short run. When we talk specifically about travel agencies, marketing your travel agencies is extremely important because it is that one particular key driver of high levels of sales. If you are unable to market your travel agency properly, you may end up losing your current customers and may lose your potential customers to your competitors.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\">One of the major and the most common marketing mistakes that are made by travel agencies are not giving enough importance to your mission and vision statements. A mission statement helps you to identify your goals and objectives as an organization and a vision statement helps you visualize your organization as a whole. If you are not clear about both of these or if you don&rsquo;t have specific vision and mission statements for your organization, you may end up creating a perception in the minds of your customers that the organization is not sure about what it wants or what it is about. If your values are not expressed accurately, your travel agency will not be able to attract more customers and might even end up losing the ones that it has already acquired. Another major benefit of having a mission and a vision statement is that helps you to identify the key elements of your organization and clears up any ambiguities that might be there in the clients&rsquo; mind. A good way to put your mission and vision statements out there is to upload them on your official website so that it is there for everyone to view.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\">Another major mistake is the inconsistency when it comes to marketing your organization. Usually, travel agencies have this perception that they only need to market their organization when they feel that they are failing in meeting the objectives that they have set for their organization. Marketing your organization efficiently and effectively requires a consistent effort because you need to make sure that your current and potential clients remember you. Your travel agency needs to market itself in such a way that it makes a lasting impression on the minds of your customers and whenever they feel the need that they require the services of a travel agency, the name of your organization should instantly pop up in their head. This can be done through advertising your travel agency through different mediums such are print, radio, television, and different social media platforms. Effective marketing and advertising are important however you also need to make sure that there is no information overload otherwise your efforts can go to waste.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\">Not having a unique selling point of your travel agency can be another major mistake that might make which will eventually cost you a lot in the long run. You need to differentiate your travel agency from that of your competitors in one way or another. Having a unique selling point can sometimes prove to be extremely attractive for the customers. Sometimes, travelers even look for that one particular quality that you have in your business that is not there in the rest of the travel agencies whom you are competing against. Simply claiming that your travel agency is better than your competitors of you can offer better quality services as compared to your competitors is not enough because every other organization makes this claim. One thing that can set you apart from the rest of the travel agencies is finding a way to quantify and give proper reasoning as to how the services that you are offering are better than that of your competitors. Furthermore, the main of your travel agency should be more on outlining and pointing out the benefits to the potential clients if they avail of your services rather than just talking about the features of your organization, your travel agency should always have a more customer-oriented approach. Being in business for a long period means that you are established but the client will never be interested in knowing the story of your organization unless it benefits them in one way or another.</span></p>\r\n', '', 1, 1, 0, 'image_750x_5e6b6a34e701e.jpg', 2479, '2020-03-13 16:30:01'),
(111, 1, 'How to affiliate and sell travel services through the website of your travel agency or your travel blog.', 'how-to-affiliate-and-sell-travel-services-through-the-website-of-your-travel-agency-or-your-travel-b', '<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\">Nowadays, almost every other travel agency has its website that is being operated on a specific team. This team involves a group of people who are specifically hired for taking care of your website and making sure that all of your current and potential clients are always updated about everything related to your travel agency. Recently, a trend has been started where people start their travel blogs. Operating a travel blog can be expensive because you are constantly traveling and keeping your audience updated about the different tourist destinations and many other things about travel, and only traveling alone can sometimes cost you an arm and a leg. A great idea would be to find a way through which you could earn through a travel blog. This article will prove to be helpful to you in finding a way to monetize your travel blog through the concept of affiliate marketing.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\">Affiliate marketing is a concept that is implemented by many people these days. In affiliate marketing, you earn money in the form of commission by promoting other people or the products or services being provided by different organizations. You can promote different products or services of the advertisers and earn through the sales that you might experience. In the case of a travel blog, you can earn through promoting services like ticket booking, tour planning and hotel reservations that are being offered by a specific travel agency. You, the publisher, is an intermediary between the advertiser which is the travel agency and the final customer to avails the services that are being promoted.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\">There are multiple different categories from which you get to choose from especially when you are running a travel blog. You can imply the concept of affiliate marketing in one specific area or you can focus on different areas of the consumer interest based on your liking. Having a wide variety to choose from is not the only advantage that you will enjoy but another major advantage is that you are bound to earn through affiliate marketing in the travel industry as this specific industry is constantly increasing. According to a study, it has been estimated that the travel industry has globally generated over 8.8 trillion dollars in the year 2018 and this amount has been increasing ever since. So, if you work intelligently enough, you can generate a good amount by doing promotions for a travel agency.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\">By now the concept of affiliate marketing may sound very attractive to you but there are some key concepts that you need to keep in mind to make sure that it is effective and that your promotions have been successful. First and foremost, you need to understand and be familiar with the basic concept of affiliate marketing. To avoid some of the very basic mistakes and save up some extra minutes. CPA Marketing and Super Affiliate Playbook are some of the courses that can help you become more familiar with the concepts of affiliate marketing. These two courses provide extremely basic information that will help you understand the general concepts of affiliate marketing.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\">The most crucial and the most important part of affiliate marketing is finding the correct programs that suit your needs and the ones that can accommodate you easily. Affiliate marketing can sound intimidating in the beginning but one the correct program has been found, it is not as complex as it sounds to the ear. You can do some of your research as there is a wide variety of programs that you can choose from but it is important to understand your needs as well for example in a pay-per-action program, you are paid according to the positive action that is a result from the customers side of your promotion and a pay-per-click program suggests that you are paid according to the number of clicks that are observed by the customers based on your promotion. It is important to do your research and explore a large number of affiliate programs that are out there to understand your needs and your requirements in the best way possible. Along with exploring the affiliate programs, you will also have to do some research to find the best affiliate network that is appropriate for the advertiser and the promotor. The affiliate network plays a role that is similar to that which is played by the affiliate marketer. The affiliate marketer is an intermediary between the final customer and the advertiser or the travel agency. Similarly, affiliate networks also play the role of an intermediary between the travel agency or the advertiser and the affiliate marketer themselves. Having a good and effective affiliate network is as important as finding the right niche for you to target or selecting the best program that suits your needs. That is because having a good affiliate network means effective, efficient and productive communication between the travel agency and the affiliate marketer. Awin, Commission Junction and Travelpayouts are some of the largest and the most effective affiliate networks being used currently.</span></p>\r\n', '', 1, 1, 0, 'image_750x_5e6a0eb97eb5e.jpg', 1134, '2020-03-12 16:30:33');
INSERT INTO `posts` (`id`, `status`, `title`, `slug`, `content`, `keywords`, `user_id`, `category_id`, `subcategory_id`, `img`, `hits`, `created_at`) VALUES
(112, 1, 'Some of the basic things that every traveler demands from a travel agency.', 'some-of-the-basic-things-that-every-traveler-demands-from-a-travel-agency', '<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\">Traveling in itself and arranging for your trip has drastically changed over the years. We are currently living in an era in which almost every person of the age of 18 or above has some kind of electronic device with them, either a smartphone, a tablet or a computer. Being dependent on so many electronic devices automatically means that the way we live our daily lives has changed a lot over the decades. This change was not only observed in our daily lives but also the world of travel industries. The travel agencies have started operating differently and this change has been observed over many years. This change was not only observed in the travel industries over the globe but changes have also been observed in the patterns of demands of the travelers. This article provides some of the factors that are considered important by travelers and what they expect from a good travel agency.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\">The first and the most important thing that a traveler seeks for in a travel agency is professional expertise. A traveler will also look up to the recommendations provided by his or her agent especially if they are planning on going on the trip that includes a lot of complexities and requires a lot of homework to be done. The traveler will expect his travel agent to advise him what is best for them and plans out a trip that is both enjoyable and lies within the budget of the traveler. It has been estimated that there is an 80 to 85 percent chance that the traveler is likely to hire a travel agent who is planning to take care of all the planning of their trip on their own. This is why the travel agency must provide the best and the most practical advice to the traveler. Also, good travel agents are trained in such a way that they can understand the needs and the requirements of their customers in the best way possible. A good travel agent will also be well aware of how to fulfill those needs and requirements along with making their customers happy lying within the budget of their respective customers.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\">People are always concerned about saving their money especially when it comes to traveling because traveling in itself can sometimes be too expensive. Generally, people have this perception that if they hire an intermediary, in this case, a travel agent, to help them plan out their entire trip for them, their costs might end up increasing because not only will they have to pay for the trip but they will also have to pay for the services that they avail that are being provided by the travel agent. This is a very big misconception that people had but now people who plan on traveling prefer to hire a travel agent to take care of all the things for the. This not only generates business for the travel agency but it also helps the traveler to save some money as the travel agents usually come up with deals and packages for their clients that are best suited to their needs. Along with saving money, by hiring a travel agent the travel does not have to worry about anything and can focus on enjoying their trip.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\">These days travelers also depend on the travel agent to take care of the little details that may have to potential to completely ruin the trip of the traveler. Weather checks or the quality of hotel rooms that are reserved for the traveler are good examples of some of the tiny matters that are handled by the travel agent. If it starts raining in the middle of the trip or if the quality of the hotel rooms is not up to the mark, the traveler may end up getting so disappointed that they feel the need to cancel the rest of their trip altogether. Travelers prefer to relay on travel agents to take care of such things and to keep them updated. Not only does this reduces the weight on the shoulders of the traveler but this also helps to save some extra minutes that can be used somewhere else by the traveler. In short, travelers prefer to have a security net that will catch them in case they fall. This also helps to develop some degree of trust and reliance between the travel agency and the customer.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\">These days, with all the modernizations and the latest technology, every person knows exactly what he or she wants. Whether it is traveling or any other decision that needs to be made in a persons&rsquo; life, all the information needed and the homework required is done beforehand. That is why travel agencies need to make sure that all the information that is required by a potential traveler can be given to them without much difficulty. A traveler will always visit the official website of the desired travel agency and the traveler will most definitely visit the websites and try to gather information about other travel agencies as well. Gathering all the relevant and useful information can be considered the right of the traveler so it is important that the website of the travel agency is always up to date and does not provide any irrelevant information. A travel agency must make sure that all the relevant information is provided on its website that its targeted audience may require. On the other hand, providing way too much information may result in information overload that may confuse the traveler and make them even more indecisive about their decisions.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', 'travel agency services, travel agency products, travel services, travel agency basic services', 1, 1, 0, 'image_750x_5e5f77dd5a3bb.jpg', 1289, '2020-03-04 16:35:47'),
(113, 1, 'PHPTRAVELS Android Native v2 APP Released', 'phptravels-android-native-v2-app-released', '<p>Good news! today we are releasing PHPTRAVELS mobile android app v2 which has new design better performance and much more including with opensource code.&nbsp;<br />\r\n<br />\r\nif you already purchased the code just login to your panel at www.phptravels.org and download the source code to compile and submit to a store</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.phptravelsnative\" target=\"_blank\">Demo APP Link&nbsp;</a></p>\r\n', 'phptraavels mobile app, phptravels android app, travel app, androidd travel app, android booking app, opensource travel android app', 1, 2, 0, 'image_750x_5e6173d148451.jpg', 1570, '2020-03-05 21:54:52'),
(114, 1, 'PHPTRAVELS partnership with iway.io ', 'phptravels-partnership-with-iwayio', '<p>PHPTRAVELS partnered with <a href=\"https://iWay.io\" target=\"_blank\">iway.io</a> worlds most airport transfer and car rental company.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>iway.io&nbsp;has partnered with PHPTRAVELS&nbsp;to provide worldwide airport transfer services for any travel agent.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Some of the benefits using the iway.io platform are that not only is it safe and convenient (24/7 real-time support) but it also gives travel agents the flexibility to set up built-in options allowing them to fully booking services to their needs.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Our partners can enjoy seamless service with iway.io, meaning that on top of using a powerful engine to cover airport transfers, travelers will also be able to check if they need another rental or process it in case they do.<br />\r\n<br />\r\niway.io API integration with PHPTRAVELS is also in process and it will be available within 2020.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>About iway.io</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>i&rsquo;way &ndash; trusted and reliable global transfer service provider. Hundreds of DMC companies and travel agencies trust us, as well as individual travelers.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>We have created this service because of the lack of up to date methods of airport meetings. Usually, driver is the first face you meet upon arrival in an alien city. So it is really important to be confident in his professionalism.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Currently, we are capable to provide the service at unified standards, fixed rates in over 670 cities.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We work to make your trip safe and comfortable as well as the booking process quick and easy. Today it takes only a few minutes to book a transfer via our website.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We are available 24/7.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Trust us and enjoy your trip!</p>\r\n', 'phptravels partnership, phptravels iway, iway.io, phptravels and iway.io', 1, 4, 0, 'image_750x_5e906d08033ab.jpg', 1172, '2020-03-10 11:57:51'),
(115, 1, 'Our commitment to you during COVID-19', 'our-commitment-to-you-during-covid-19', '<p>With all of the news surrounding coronavirus (COVID-19), we&nbsp;wanted to communicate directly with our seller community about what we&rsquo;re doing to ensure the <strong>PHPTRAVELS </strong>platform remains operational during this disruptive time.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We are here to serve you, our sellers, and we want to be transparent with you regarding our plans to operate safely and effectively. Our thoughts are with everyone affected by the coronavirus.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We understand <strong>PHPTRAVELS </strong>plays an integral role in the operations of our seller&rsquo;s businesses, and we appreciate the trust you place in us as your full-service eCommerce partner. We are taking proactive steps to ensure we have a fully supported infrastructure and plans in place to maintain the functionality of our platform while prioritizing the health of our employees. We have the ability to run all aspects of our business on a remote basis in the event that employees are unable to physically be present in our offices, and we are performing tests of such ability to ensure our readiness.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We are following the World Health Organization (WHO) and the Center for Disease Control (CDC) for updates and directives regarding coronavirus.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We do not expect any disruptions to our services, and you can always check the status of the <strong>PHPTRAVELS </strong>&nbsp;platform by visiting the <a href=\"https://phptravels.com\">https://www.phptravels.com</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>As the situation develops, we will continue monitoring the news. Throughout this unfortunate event, we are committed to maintaining the functionality of our platform and the delivery of our services for our sellers.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I want to personally thank you for your continued support as a valued member of the <strong>PHPTRAVELS </strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Sincerely,</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Qasim Hussain&nbsp;<br />\r\nCEO&nbsp;<strong>PHPTRAVELS </strong></p>\r\n', 'covid-19 travel industry, corona virus travel industry, carona travel, carona disruptions ', 1, 4, 0, 'image_750x_5e6a17ba907b0.jpg', 1221, '2020-03-13 11:02:54'),
(116, 1, 'We Are Ready to Support You', 'we-are-ready-to-support-you', '<p>These are not easy times for travel businesses. If your business is affected by these extraordinary circumstances, PHPTRAVELS wants to support you as much as possible. When the online travel industry is taking the lead, we will do our best to help you stay connected with your customers, no matter where you may be working.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Our company has, just like many others, switched to remote work. Because of that, we know that it&rsquo;s even more important to stay coordinated and provide instant information. Remember that our support team is available 24/7 to help you with every product problem and question you might have. At the same time, we would like to assure you that your business is safe with us. All our products and infrastructure are up and running as usual. All operations, including product development and support, are running like normal.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Additionally, there are several initiatives that we&rsquo;ve taken:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We support nonprofit organizations supporting the community, especially during this time of need. Such organizations can apply for&nbsp;<strong>PHPTRAVELS&nbsp;</strong>for Nonprofits and get our product for free. (For-profits organizations can apply if they can show that they support others). If you need our help, or if you know an organization that could benefit from it, please let us know.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>For all companies that need to switch to remote work. Additionally, we can offer a 50% discount for your first purchase and this discount will be applicable during this situation.&nbsp;<br />\r\n<br />\r\nDespite the circumstances, we want to make sure that you can manage your workflow effectively. Our Support Heroes are more ready than ever to help you adjust to the challenges of this unique situation and to assist you in getting the most out of all of our products.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Our priority is, and will always be, the wellbeing of our team and customers. We believe that by implementing these initiatives, we can help to keep you, your team, and customers safe, along with your business.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Best&nbsp;<br />\r\n<strong>Team PHPTRAVELS</strong></p>\r\n', '', 1, 4, 0, 'image_750x_5e70c05a12137.jpg', 1404, '2020-03-17 12:17:12'),
(117, 1, 'Coronavirus: How we\'re staying safe', 'coronavirus-how-were-staying-safe', '<p>Hi Dear ?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>How&#39;s it going? Hope you&#39;re staying safe during the COVID-19 outbreak.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This week&#39;s&nbsp;special issue dedicated to the&nbsp;safety precautions that phptravels have taken&nbsp;as a company to prevent the spread of the Coronavirus.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://phptravels.com/blog/uploads/images/image_750x415_5e748e5fe6e16.jpg\" style=\"height:415px; width:750px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>PHPTRAVELS has granted all our employees the right to work from home. Accordingly, our physical offices have closed until further notice. We have taken this step with the social responsibility to safeguard our community from being exposed to any additional risk of infection and danger.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Read our&nbsp;blog post&nbsp;on how we have managed to make remote working effective and efficient.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Try your best to give remote working a chance. The social responsibility you show today will have a drastic effect on tomorrow.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>See you next week with another special update..&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Stay safe, stay aware and stay indoors.</p>\r\n', 'coronavirus, coronavirus remote work, work from home, covid 19 work from home culture', 1, 4, 0, 'image_750x_5e748e27c4d4d.jpg', 1277, '2020-03-20 09:40:20'),
(118, 1, 'PHPTRAVELS  50% Special Offer Today', 'phptravels-50-special-offer-today', '<p>We understand how COVID-19 affected the travel industry, therefore, we are here today announcing 50% discount on all our products to help you grow and benefit from this offer today.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In this hard time, we want to launch / start-up your online travel business and take full advantage of the current situation. and work on your brand marketing business strategy and booking engine. to offer the best travel services once the market is back normal.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>No coupon code needed no promo required simply just visit our order page from below button and get your discount applied straight away.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\n<a class=\"btn btn-danger btn-lg\" href=\"https://phptravels.com/order\" style=\"color:#fff\" target=\"_blank\">Claim Discount</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'phptravels discount, phptravels promo, phptravels cheap, phptravels free, phptravels download', 1, 5, 0, 'image_750x_5e7d4b9274de7.jpg', 1170, '2020-03-27 00:42:25'),
(119, 1, 'How has COVID-19 corona affected and is affecting the travel industry?', 'how-has-covid-19-corona-affected-and-is-affecting-the-travel-industry', '<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">Our precious planet is, unfortunately, going through a very big calamity these days. The Coronavirus, also known as COVID-19, has greatly affected our lives negatively and is continuing to do so. It has affected the pattern of our lives which includes traveling. The spread of coronavirus initially started in December of 2019 and since then it has spread and victimized people from over 20 countries. The situation that is being dealt with right now is pretty similar to that of 2003 when there was a SARS outbreak in China which greatly affected the tourism industry of that particular country. In today&#39;s world, tourism is a very big industry that greatly contributes to the GDP and the economies of different areas. According to a credible source, approximately 10.4 percent of the GDP is generated through the tourism industry along with 10 percent of global employment. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">With the spread of the coronavirus all over Europe, Asia, the United States, the Middle East and other parts of the globe, people are questioning their decisions about traveling because of the fright they have that they might end up contracting the disease. People are avoiding traveling and are preferring to cancel their plans instead of going along with them and risking their health. Strict rules have been implemented throughout the airports globally and the body temperature of every passenger is individually being checked. However, there still is a slight risk, because higher body temperatures are not the only symptom of catching this virus. There are many more symptoms which include dry cough, tiredness and body aches. The spread of coronavirus has greatly accelerated because of healthy people contracting the virus from the patients.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">With the continuous levels of acceleration of this particular virus, strict bans have been implemented when it comes to traveling to or from the countries of China, Iran, Italy, and South Korea. These bans have been implemented by the CDC. The same agency has also given warnings to travelers and has implemented rules of lower strictness levels on traveling to or from other countries. If a person is traveling in such a situation, first and foremost, they should be well informed and do their research on the disease control centers of that particular area. If that country is well equipped and if the traveler takes all the precautionary measures, they are unlikely to contract the disease.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">In case a person has already booked a trip that they may want to cancel because of the global pandemic that is going on, </span></span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">there is a very high level of possibility that you may not get the entire amount refunded that you initially invested on your trip. The decision that has to be made regarding traveling or canceling the trip, however, solely depends on you and your preferences. You might end up getting a refund if your final destination is China, Iran, Italy or any of the areas of the world whose majority of the population has contracted the virus but all depends on the airline that you chose. The best idea in such a situation would be to constantly be in touch with your travel agency and ask them to keep providing you with constant updates.z</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">When it comes to the effects on the global travel industry because of the coronavirus, the first and the most obvious one is the way it has affected the imports and exports of different countries. Because of the coronavirus, people have started to fear trading with other countries as they feel that the products that are being exchanged might end up bringing the virus in their countries. Secondly, businessmen who solely relied on traveling for business purposes are continuously suffering because of this virus. That is mainly because of the ban that has been implemented in different countries by different governments. A good example could be Pakistan and China. A lot of raw material for the clothing industry in Pakistan comes from China, but ever since the spread of coronavirus accelerated in China and ended up spreading into different countries, the imports from China of the raw material for clothing has completely stopped. Because of this, not only is the clothing industry of Pakistan suffering but also the businessmen and owners of different factories that manufacture clothes. Because of this, people are losing their jobs and the economy, in general, is greatly suffering.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">When we talk about traveling for leisure purposes or booking a trip with your loved ones, if you have already booked and are confused about deciding if you should travel or not, the best idea would be to talk to your travel agent and get in touch with the airline directly. Airlines are quite flexible these days, because of the global pandemic, as they would not want to lose their clients and are offering different ways and solutions to people who want a change in their plans. For example, Jet Blue is not charging its customers who plan on changing their traveling plans from February 27<sup>th,</sup> 2020 up to March 11<sup>th,</sup> 2020 for travel completed by June 1<sup>st,</sup> 2020. The best approach, however, would be to wait and watch if the situation gets better and the spread of the coronavirus is brought under the control of not before planning on traveling.</span></span></p>\r\n', '', 1, 1, 0, 'image_750x_5e8ecc1d049cf.jpg', 1236, '2020-04-09 06:57:18'),
(123, 1, 'The future of travel technology', 'the-future-of-travel-technology', '<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">Technology has transformed the way we view different things in our lives. A few decades ago, people used to communicate with each other through letters which would sometimes take months. Now, we can send a text message to our employees or loved ones within a matter of a few seconds. A major part of our lives is traveling, along with the rest of the things, technology has completely transformed that part of our lives as well. We, however, have benefitted from the change that has been resulted by technological advancements because of the high levels of personalization and convenience offered to us.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">Artificial intelligence has started to play an extremely important role in our lives especially when it comes to traveling. Almost a decade ago, the concept of artificial intelligence and the usage of robotics in the travel industry seemed to be extremely bizarre, unrealistic and futuristic but nowadays, different airports and airlines have started to incorporate this particular concept within their organizations and have also started seeking many benefits out of it. It is, however, a little expensive and requires a large amount of initial investment but the benefits that different organizations are enjoying by employing them completely cover up the initial cost that they had to pay in the form of investment. When we talk about traveling, one of the biggest barriers that are usually faced by people is the language barrier and robotics have made it easy for people to overcome this particular barrier. Moreover, these robots also help to cut down the cost of the organization, let it be an airport or an airline, because they do not have to pay more people to do that particular job. Schiphol airport and Geneva airport have already introduced robotics into their systems and have greatly benefitted from them. These robots help in guiding people about the flights, recognize the emotions of the customers and are designed in a way to cope up with any unexpected situation that may arise.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">One of the most common complaints that people nowadays have is the inconvenience that they have to face when they lose or misplace their luggage. But thanks to all the technological advances, a very good solution to this problem has also been generated. Smart baggage solutions will not only help the travelers with their luggage and in helping them avoid all the inconvenience that they might have to face but it will also help the airports with saving a lot of money and time. The airport staff that gets busy is helping the traveler find their luggage might save all the time and use it in assisting other travelers who might be facing even bigger inconveniences. The new biometric enabled bag drop can prove to be an extremely useful device for people who travel frequently and are always on the go.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">Someone who is a big fan of traveling is also likely to be a big fan of photography and capturing different moments for them to enjoy later. During the past few years, people have started using drones to help them capture all the moments that they enjoy so that they can live in those moments later on. Drones have played a big role in traveling and photography they have helped the travel industry to grow even more. That is because people share almost everything on their social media accounts such as Facebook and Instagram, and esthetically appealing pictures attract more people to that particular destination where the picture was originally captured. This is an advantage for the travel agencies as it helps them to generate more business and earn more revenues.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">The concept of virtual reality is another interesting concept that has risen over the past few years. It helps the potential traveler to experience the landscape and the history of a particular destination from the ease of their living rooms. Not only travel agencies have benefitted from them but many other organizations have also benefitted from them through the art of providing the demanded experience and through the art of story-telling. Virtual reality is a great way through which travel agencies can work more efficiently by planning the trip of their clients in a better way, this will not only satisfy the client and increase the levels of customer loyalty but it will also help the travel agencies to generate more business. Other organizations in different sectors have also started to adopt the concept of virtual reality by creating websites that provide 360-degree video and photography.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">Overall, technology has played a major role in the travel industries all over the world. With the continuous discoveries that are being made, the level of technological advancements is also increasing day by day. Thanks to the technological advancements in the travel industries globally, the travel sector has profited a lot and is continuously profiting from it.</span></span></p>\r\n', 'travel technology, future of travel industry, how travel future, travel industry future', 1, 6, 0, 'image_750x_5f7f253d0d469.jpg', 724, '2020-10-08 07:03:05'),
(124, 1, 'How to choose a GDS, Global Distribution System, for your travel business.', 'how-to-choose-a-gds-global-distribution-system-for-your-travel-business', '<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">Global distribution systems are an extremely important and integral part of the tourism and travel industry. That is because it helps the travel agency and all the other organizations, such as hotels and airlines, keep track of everything. It gives the major advantage of personalization that can be enjoyed and also helps to generate more and more revenues. Since everything is kept organized and all the information related to the client is constantly being saved, thanks to the global distribution systems, is it a lot easier for the organization to offer what the client wants according to his or her preferences. Every travel business requires a good global distribution system that caters to all of its needs and requirements, this article highlights some of the ways that could greatly help your travel business to choose the most suitable global distribution system according to its needs and requirements and also highlights some of the benefits of investing in a global distribution system.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">One of the most common problems that travel businesses have to face if they do not have a global distribution system within their organization is the amount of time that is consumed on simple things such as gathering important information from the official website of the airline or the hotel with which your travel business is affiliated It has been estimated that 54 percent of travel agents spend at least 30 minutes per day from their time on the website and approximately 26 percent of the travel agents spend more than an hour per day. If a good global distribution system is invested in, all of this time could be saved and could be utilized in something more useful. The biggest advantage of a good global distribution system would be generating more revenues by upselling the services being offered, capturing every sales opportunity and increasing the level of brand loyalty by providing faster and more efficient services.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">The needs and requirements of every business organization are different so it is extremely important to be very well aware of what your travel business requires before deciding whether or not you have to invest in a particular global distribution system. Mentioned below are some of the characteristics and features that should be present in the global distribution system before you decide to invest in it.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">The global distribution system that you choose to invest in should be capable enough to let you customize the services that you plan on offering to your respective clients. This is extremely important because every client is different and the needs and requirements of every other are also different. You can&rsquo;t offer the same service with the same features to all of your clients. That is why is it extremely important that you invest in such a global distribution system that helps you to customize the services for each customer. This will also help you, as a travel agent, to save a lot of time as all of the information will be provided on a single platform and you would not have to go back and forth to gather all the information to design a suitable package for your client.</span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">There are some very basic features that every business needs to have to be successful, generate more revenues and every earns higher levels of profits. When it comes to travel businesses, one of these main features includes high levels of efficiency and value maximization. To increase the levels of your travel business, it is important to make sure that the global distribution system that you are planning on investing in is up to date with all the technological advancements going on around us. That is important because it will drastically increase and improve the efficiency levels of your organization which will, at the end of the day, save up more time and ensures a happy and satisfied customer leading to higher levels of customer loyalty. An up to date global distribution will speed up the booking system of your organization, it will help you in responding to your clients without taking up a lot of time and it will provide you will enough flexibility to personalize the services according to your clients&#39; requirements.</span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">One of the most important features that you should look for before deciding to invest in a global distribution system should be its ability to update without disrupting your workflow or slowing down the pace at which all the work is being done at your organization. This is extremely important because in case your selected software needs an update but during the update, all the work that you have been putting in is disrupted and all the information is lost, a lot of inconveniences might be created for you. Your travel business might not be able to provide your client with the service on time and you might end up losing the client altogether. It is important to make sure that the global distribution system selected for your business is advanced enough to update automatically without slowing down your business which might result in a loss of revenues.</span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', 'How to choose a GDS. best GDS, selecting GDS, how to find GDS, what is GDS, GDS registration', 1, 1, 0, 'image_750x_5ea9cfac9ea8f.jpg', 1421, '2020-04-29 07:03:44'),
(125, 1, 'What is a DMS, Distribution Management System?', 'what-is-a-dms-distribution-management-system', '<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">Everything is happening at a very fast pace in the travel industry. No hurdles are expected to be there when the organization is operating because the more the hurdles an organization has to face, the more bottlenecks they will experience in their workflow. From generating demand from the desired target market to designing services for them and communicating with them, a smooth pattern or a path is required which is followed by every organization. Any hurdles that are observed in that particular path may result in a lot of inconveniences and disturbances such as delays in the service being provided, miscommunication between the service provider and the client, and overall a dissatisfied and unhappy client. To avoid all of these problems and to achieve the efficiency and effectiveness of your organization, it is important to invest in a good distribution management system that aids your organization and fulfills all of its needs and requirements.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">A distribution management system is a set of different software and applications that generally help your organization with designing, monitoring and controlling the entire distribution system of your organization in a way that is not effective, efficient and not very time-consuming. It also helps you to keep track of your current level and the desired level of your inventories and helps you to monitor and have stronger control over the supply chain of your organization. A distribution management system also helps you to monitor the electric supply within your organization which can help you to avoid any bottlenecks that may result in the shortages. It helps you keep track of the voltage that is provided and the frequency which helps to minimize the outage period.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">Having a good distribution management system is extremely crucial for almost every organization these days, that is because a big part of how your business operates depends on the type of distribution management system in which you invest along with the effectiveness and the efficiency of its functioning. One of the major advantages that your organization will be able to enjoy is going to be the reduction in the outages that your company might experience as compared to the number of outrages that it will experience without the distribution management system. Having a longer period of outages means that all your activities and all of the effort and work being put into meeting your goals in going to waste, so you must invest in a system that saves you from going through the hassle of doing all the work all over again. Especially if you have a travel business, you must have a suitable distribution management system because you cannot afford any bottlenecks that may affect your work and may end up resulting in a delay of service that was initially offered. That is because you are dealing with multiple different parts of the final service that is offered, for example, hotel reservation and flight booking. Having a slight inconvenience can mean that the entire procedure of planning a trip for your client will be delayed.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">Another major advantage of having a suitable distribution management system is that all your work and the backstage activities of your organization, which are essential in providing the services, will speed up. This can potentially mean that you will take a lot lesser time in finalizing everything and providing the final service to your respective clients as compared to before. People appreciate if the service that they desire is being offered to them on the promised time and that there are no delays. So, having a speedy system can be a big advantage for your organization because that just means that your client is happy and satisfied with what you have offered them. This also means that higher levels of customer loyalty can be expected which will eventually help you in generating more business and as a result, more profits.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">Having an efficient distribution management system can also help the management of your organization allocate the resources available in a better and more efficient way. This just means that you can allocate new resources in different departments of your organization as you will have a better understanding of the particular needs and requirements of your organization, and you can re-allocate the current resources to gain the most out of them. That way, you will have more outcomes from your organization and you will also end up saving some money as no available resources will be going to waste. The scheduling of your organization can also be done according to you the outage timings as you will be well aware of thanks to the distribution management system.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">Like every human being, different organizations and businesses also have different needs and requirements that help them to sustain and survive in extremely competitive markets. Similarly, a good distribution management system is also a requirement for businesses these days because, without it, your organization will encounter a lot of inconveniences that will harm it in the short and the long run.</span></span></p>\r\n', 'dms, distribution management system, distribute management, how to distribute, best distribute system management, distribution software', 1, 1, 0, 'image_750x_5f6c5c8ae8c2d.jpg', 732, '2020-09-25 07:06:11'),
(126, 1, 'How does a PMS Property Management System work?', 'how-does-a-pms-property-management-system-work', '<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">Managing a hotel chain can sometimes prove to be extremely stressful. There are a lot of things that you need to consider and think about that can make things a lot harder for you. Handling the front stage tasks is very difficult because you are dealing with so many different people and since every person is different, you need to understand how to deal with people and make sure that they are satisfied with what you are offering to them. Something that is even difficult is handling and taking care of the backstage activities. To make their life easier, people have started investing in property management systems. Property management systems can prove to be extremely effective if you are looking for a way to take care of your backstage activities. If you invest in a property management system that is suitable according to your needs and requirements, it will effectively be able to take care of backstage activities such as keeping track of the inventories, bookings, check-ins, check-outs, recording all the important data about the customer and generate reports about the performance of your property. It will also help you to carry out all the activities that take place daily in an efficient way. These activities can include effective communication, reservations, handling your accounts and maintenance and housekeeping.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">A property management system consists of two main parts, the first one is the booking engine and the second part is the channel manager. Firstly, let us talk about the booking engine, then we shall move on to the channel manager. A good way of describing a booking engine can be a system that helps to make more reservations and helps you in the process of making more bookings. We are currently living in a world in which everything can be done within a few seconds in a matter of a few clicks, so in this age and era, it is extremely important to have a system that can help with boosting your business and helps you in generating more business, that is why it is important to have a booking engine that can aid your need of online booking.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">Channel managers are also a system that can help you take care and keep track of all the inventories of the different businesses with which you are affiliated. They are mostly useful for online travel agencies because the channel managers can help the online travel agencies to keep all the records of inventories of airlines, hotels, etc. This is also very helpful because it gives you a better understanding of how much capacity is left and how much more business you need to generate to cover up your costs.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">It is always a good idea to invest in a property management system. Initially, it might sound like something extremely intimidating but investing in a suitable property management system is always a good idea. Because at first, it may seem not very reasonable to spend money but as your organization starts to grow, it might cost you even more. The first sign that you need a property management system is that you are unable to save all the data. This system can prove to be of great help as it will store all the data and can help you analyze the needs and requirements of your customers a little better. That way you will know exactly what or what not you have to offer them. This can also help you to generate more business as your system will be more responsive and the level of your customer satisfaction will increase. As your customers will be satisfied with the services that they are availing, they will be more loyal to your organization. These systems can also help you to have better communication with your clients. Since all the important information and data will be saved through these systems, you will know exactly when and how to keep each of your customers engaged to your organization along with making sure that they are always up to date and responsive. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">These days, time is money. That is because you can earn money if you choose to spend your time effectively and efficiently. These property management systems can prove to be of great help when you are planning on saving time. That is because you would not have to go through the hassle of searching for the important data as it will already be saved in the system and you will know exactly how much time needs to be allocated on what. Since these systems can help you have a better insight into the performance of your organization, they can also aid you in making better decisions about the changes that need to be made or the areas in which your organization is lacking as compared to your competitor. Considering all of these factors, it can be extremely profitable to invest in a good property management system that is suitable for the needs and requirements of your organization.</span></p>\r\n', 'pms management, property management system solutions, best pms, easy pms, pms opensource solution', 1, 1, 0, 'image_750x_5f62102f01e71.jpg', 688, '2020-09-17 07:06:48');
INSERT INTO `posts` (`id`, `status`, `title`, `slug`, `content`, `keywords`, `user_id`, `category_id`, `subcategory_id`, `img`, `hits`, `created_at`) VALUES
(127, 1, 'What is the best CM, channel manager, for your hotel?', 'what-is-the-best-cm-channel-manager-for-your-hotel', '<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">Over the decades, many different and extremely interesting technological advancements have been observed and enjoyed. Similarly, many of these technological advancements were in the field of traveling and the travel industry in general. One of these technological advancements in the Channel Manager that has been invented for even further convenience. The channel manager is a technology that has been created mainly for large hotel chains. Channel managers help and aid the hotels in managing the hotel overall, it helps in saving a lot of time and it also helps in maximizing profits. Profit maximization is one of the main aims and objectives of every other organization regardless of what field it is operating in, that is why channel managers are extremely attractive for the people who run hotel chains. But not only profit maximization, but it also has many other benefits such as expanding the reach of their hotels and increasing the levels of occupancy.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">One of the greatest advantages of having a channel manager within your organization is that it gets extremely easy for you to manage all your inventories and keep all the other organizations updated that are affiliated with you. What this means is that it saves up a lot of time and hassle that you might have to put into your organization to keep everything updated. For example, if your hotel is affiliated with a particular travel agency, it is important to keep that particular travel agency updated about the level of your inventories to avoid any inconveniences such as overbooking. Having a channel manages also saves up a lot of time as everything will be automated and nothing will be done manually along with saving a lot of hassle and thought. Another big advantage of investing in a channel manager is that it gives you a lot of power and authority to make decisions that are best for your hotel. It also removes the factor of unpredictability. For example, you will know exactly how much revenues are allocated to what part of your organization, that way you can make better decisions about revenue allocation and come up with different strategies that can benefit your organization in the short and long run.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">Approximately 50 percent of the hotels worldwide use some sort of channel manager. If your hotel is planning on investing in a channel manager, some important factors need to be considered before making this decision. The first and most important factor that needs to be taken under consideration is the level of connectivity between your hotel and different intermediaries along with the efficiency and effectiveness of the communication that is taking place between them. If you are unable to communicate and connect with your supplier, different airlines and travel agencies, that means that you need to come up with a system that keeps people within your organization and people within the affiliated organizations constantly up to date. One of the main reasons why this is so important is that removes the factor of uncertainty and helps you avoid overbooking. It also helps you keep track of all of your inventories and helps you manage them better.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">Another major factor that needs to be considered is the size and the occupation of your property. What this means is that the size of your hotel will have a massive impact on the operations and how different things are being looked after. In other words, the larger your property is, the harder it is to make decisions about it and making sure that everything is running smoothly. This is an extremely important factor because if your hotel chain is very large, it is most likely earning a large number of profits but on the other hand, it is also a possibility that making decisions is equally, or even more, harder than it would have if your hotel chain was not that vast. This also means that even a single incorrect decision of yours or even the smallest of the mistakes can have a very big impact on your hotel chain. Having that said, it is important to analyze the size of your property and then invest in an appropriate hotel manager to improve your decision-making skills and avoiding all the problems or errors that could result in negative consequences that your hotel might have to face.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">You should be very well aware of the needs and requirements of your hotel along with all the errors that need to be corrected to make a wise decision about choosing the appropriate channel manager. You should always make sure that the channel manager you choose consists of three main factors which are the following</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">Property management system &ndash; This can help you gather and save all the data. A property management system is extremely important as it is the hub of a channel manager.</span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">Revenue management system &ndash; This will help you keep track of the revenues being earned in a specific period along with the level of profitability of your organization.</span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">Central reservation system &ndash; This can help you in keeping track of your inventories and can greatly help in avoiding the problem of overbooking.</span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">If all of these three systems are a part of the channel manager that you choose and if the chosen channel manager is meeting all the needs and requirements of your hotel, then you have most likely made a wise and correct decision regarding investing in an appropriate channel manager.</span></span></p>\r\n', 'best channel manager, channel manager for hotel, how to find channel manager, free channel manager, booking channel manager for ota', 1, 1, 0, 'image_750x_5ec6585d42944.jpg', 1357, '2020-05-21 07:08:28'),
(128, 1, 'How is Airbnb beating the hotel industry?', 'how-is-airbnb-beating-the-hotel-industry', '<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">The world of hotels is growing day by day and the number of hotels in different parts of the world is also growing day by day. Investing in a hotel has always been considered profitable because the tourism industry is constantly growing and the love for traveling is also growing in peoples&rsquo; hearts. This means that people will naturally require a place to live in that also provides different services such as restaurant and entertainment areas. Because of this constantly growing demand, people are showing interest in investing in hotels and this industry is growing day by day. However, since 2008, there has been a massive threat to hotels all over the world. That threat is Airbnb. Saving money always seems a good idea and people are always up for saving some extra bucks, keeping this in mind, Airbnb has successfully captured a big chunk of the revenues and profits that were once earned by the hotels. Because of this, hotels have had to suffer a lot.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">A study conducted showed that with the hotel bookings decreasing because of Airbnb, Airbnb captured 1.3 percent of the market share that once belonged to the hotels which resulted in the hotels suffering a massive chunk, 1.5 percent, of their revenues. These numbers have not remained the same ever since the data was evaluated but have increased dramatically over the last five years. The majority of the market, approximately 10 to 12 percent according to one study, that has been captured by Airbnb is in New York City, London, and Paris. This data is only constricted to The United States of America. If we consider the data from different hotels globally, then the numbers are even larger. Losses in revenues and profits are the main reason why Airbnb is considered to be the biggest enemy of the hotel industry.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">The average price of the services offered through Airbnb is a lot lower and economical as compared to the services that are being offered at a regular hotel. Earning money through fair means in today&#39;s world is extremely hard and difficult so people are always looking for different ways through which they can save some bucks that can be later on used somewhere else. One of the main attractions for travelers for using Airbnb is that they will be saving a lot of money if they choose Airbnb over a hotel. Another main reason for choosing Airbnb over hotels is that traveling in itself is extremely costly and expensive. There are several factors that you need to consider before planning a trip which includes spending money on food, outings, the money spend to purchase the flight tickets and fees of the travel agent. Amongst all these big expenses, saving up some money always seems a good idea. Moreover, the core services being offered by hotels and Airbnb and pretty much the same so another reason why people end up choosing Airbnb over regular hotels is that they only consider the core services that are being offered to them and completely ignore the supplementary services that come with the core services in a hotel. For example, services such as the access to the pool or the gymnasium are not offered in Airbnb, however, they are offered at different hotels.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">With the increase in demand for the services being provided by Airbnb, customers automatically end up expecting that the quality of the services that they are about to pay for will also be good. The quality of the services being provided through Airbnb is increasing as compared to that of the hotels, this has resulted in the customer not even considering staying in a hotel. The reason for that is that is has become a lot easier for the potential customers to draw a comparison between the two and make their final decision which is, majority of the time, in favor of Airbnb. The rates of Airbnb are also increasing between they are still substantially lower than that of the hotels so when the customers draw a comparison between Airbnb and the hotel they were thinking of choosing, they do not even consider the rise in prices of the services being provided through Airbnb since they are still lower than that of the good hotels of that particular area.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">Since Airbnb has constantly been capturing the market shares of the hotels in different parts of the world, it has become harder for the hotels to earn revenues which have automatically resulted in a decrease in the profitability of the overall hotel industry. Because of this, the profit margins of the hotels have been decreased and it has become even harder for these hotels to cover up their costs. So, to avoid any financial losses and to cover up their costs in an effective way, the prices and rate of the services being provided at the hotels have increased which are expected to be borne by the final consumer. As a result, the difference between the prices of hotels and services provided through Airbnb has increased even more which has resulted in more and more people being attracted to and considering Airbnb over hotels.</span></span></p>\r\n', '', 1, 1, 0, 'image_750x_5eb1790e925a9.jpg', 1177, '2020-05-05 07:09:16'),
(129, 1, 'Different ways to build a multi-billion dollar travel agency.', 'different-ways-to-build-a-multi-billion-dollar-travel-agency', '<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">With all the technological advances around us, it does not matter where we are working from. Money can be earned in many different ways and through many different sources. One of them is through establishing your travel agency. We are currently living in the world in which having a presence through any of the social media platforms such as Facebook, Twitter or Instagram is considered to be important. If you do not have a social media presence, your existence can be questioned as you are not putting yourself out in the world. As people have started to increasingly depend on their social media presence, they fell the constant need to post everything and anything that they may find interesting.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">This includes sharing their pictures and tagging all the different locations that they have visited. Especially when a person is traveling, they feel obligated to post as many pictures as possible as they have the attracted to getting the most number of likes and comments on their posts which means that they are appreciated and accepted by the people around them. Because of the constant updates being provided by travelers on social media, more and more people are attracted to travel as well. This is the main reason why the demand for traveling the tourism industry is constantly increasing. Another reason for this constant increase is the attractive tourist destinations that people want to visit.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">It would be extremely intelligent if one takes full advantage of this constantly increasing demand which could prove to be extremely profitable in the short and the long run. That is where establishing a travel agency comes into play. The first and the most important thing that you need to do in understand the market in which you will be operating. What this means is that it is extremely important to understand the demand that you are aiming to generate and, more importantly, your competitors in the market. Usually what happens is that the large, well-established, travel agencies completely wipe out the new smaller travel agencies in the market. That is why it is important to know who you will be working for and competing against. It is also important to highlight and establish your short term and long term goals and objectives in the initial stages so that you are clear about what you plan on achieving.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">Next comes identifying the different market segments and making a decision about which segments does your organization wants to target. Studying and understanding your target market and target audience is extremely important because a lot of your important decisions will depend on the targeted audience. The most important decision that you will have to make is the prices that you set for the services that you will be offering. This is important because you want to come up with a pricing strategy that will help you to successfully compete against your competitors and at the same time also allows your organization to grow and earn revenues. Pricing is the most essential part of any organization because it is the only long-lasting way for you to earn revenues and generate more and more profits. However, it is also important to make sure that your prices are not so high that you drive your potential clients a way to your competitors.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">How you introduce your travel agency to the world can also greatly impact the level of success or failure of your travel agency in the future. Marketing your travel agency is extremely important because unless you put your travel agency out there in the world, you will not receive any demand which means that you will have no way of generating any revenues. Marketing and advertising your travel agency can be done in several ways but positive word of mouth and social media marketing has proved to be the most effective ways as we are living in a completely digitized era. Most of the time, when an organization is new to the market, the use of well-known people such as bloggers and influencers is made. This is done because these bloggers and influencers usually have a large number of people following them on their social media accounts, and people also trust what they say.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">It is also important to design the services that you are offering in such a way that it helps you in generating more revenues, fulfills the demand of the customers and gives you an edge over your competitors in the market. To do that, the ideas that are birthed within your travel agency must be extremely innovative and different. Another important thing that should be kept in mind is that the umbrella of your organization should be very big which covers most of the services. This is important because your clients will feel that their money is being valued and that they are getting the most out of what they paid for.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">Once all of these steps are taken, managing your travel agency is extremely important and if not done correctly, your travel agency can fall apart. Thanks to technological advancements, much different software have been developed that can help in managing your travel agency. Initially, investing in software that suits your organization may seem a little intimidating as they usually come with a big price tag, but in the long run, they can prove to be extremely helpful and can end up cutting some of the costs of your travel agency.</span></span></p>\r\n', '', 1, 1, 0, 'image_750x_5ea045eaa6747.jpg', 1152, '2020-04-22 07:09:43'),
(130, 1, 'What are the requirements that need to be completed to start your travel agency?', 'what-are-the-requirements-that-need-to-be-completed-to-start-your-travel-agency', '<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">Before establishing and introducing business in the market, some factors need to be taken into consideration. These factors include the current situation of the economy, the expected growth of your organization, its&rsquo; expected profitability and the level of competition that you might have to face. Considering all of these factors is important because they will help you make all the important decisions about your business before you even start it, which will help it in growing and being successful in the future. Similarly, other than these important factors that need to be taken into consideration, many other factors have also been to be considered which include all the legal formalities that need to be completed. First and foremost, you need to understand and study the different options that you have of different business structures. This is important because the structure of your travel agency will help you in evaluating the taxation system of your business.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">The two most common business structures in the world of travel industries include a limited liability company, LLC, and a sole proprietorship. Most of the people who are considering opening a travel agency of their own are usually attracted more towards the option of a limited liability company. The main reason for that is that the owner of a limited liability company can be shared and you can go into partnership with 2 to 20 other parties. Another major benefit of starting a limited liability company is that you don&rsquo;t have to bear the losses on your own and they are shared amongst all the parties that are involved. However, on the other hand, a slight disadvantage is that the profits of a limited liability company are also shared. A sole proprietorship business is the one in which the ownership of the business belongs to a single person. For some people, who want to start on a smaller scale, it is considered to be a safer and easier option because it does not require a lot of legal formalities that need to be taken care of. Another advantage of a sole proprietorship is that you can start small and as your business starts to grow, and as it gets more profitable, you can expand it by turning it into a limited liability company. An employee identification number, EIN, however, is required to start a sole proprietorship.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">Getting your bookings done or planning your trip through a travel agency is not a very big hassle these days since a lot of the process that goes into it has been made easier for us and a lot of hassle has been taken care of. However, there is a lot that goes into a travel agency before it is successfully established in the market and before it starts earning profits that you could enjoy. Your travel agency should be recognized and established through certain institutions and organizations before can be established. These organizations include The Airline Reporting Corporation and International Airlines Travel Agents Network. The International Airlines Travel Agents Network has been more popular amongst the travel industries over the past 25 years approximately, however it does charge an annual fee of approximately 195 American dollars.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">As mentioned above, one of the major advantages of having an organization that has the structure of sole proprietorship is that there are not many legal formalities that need to be completed to start your own business or establish your organization. Having that said, it is not necessary to be accredited by The Airline Reporting Corporation or the International Airlines Travel Agents Network. However, not being recognized by these organizations can cost you an arm and a leg in the long run. It is always a good idea to be recognized and accredited by these organizations because that way, the commission will be paid to you by the suppliers for booking the products or services being offered by them. However, your organization or travel agency will be required to make a certain amount of sales before it is accredited. This is the main reason why the majority of the new travel agencies usually start by working with a host travel agency. This means that the new travel agency enters into a partnership with a travel agency that has already been established in the market and is already accredited by The Airline Reporting Corporation or the International Airline Travel Agents Network.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">Once all of these procedures have been taken care of, it is extremely important to market and advertises your travel agency appropriately so that you can generate demand for your organization. A good way of marketing and advertising your travel agency can be through getting your travel agency registered on TripAdvisor, Yelp, MakeMyTrip, and Google. Another helpful way can be social media advertising, which means advertising through different social media platforms such as Instagram, Facebook, and Twitter or asking your respective clients to post different reviews of the services they availed that are being offered by your travel agency.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '', 1, 1, 0, 'image_750x_5e981c0845ff7.jpg', 1308, '2020-04-16 07:10:27'),
(131, 1, 'Different ways in which the local travel industries are evolving globally.', 'different-ways-in-which-the-local-travel-industries-are-evolving-globally', '<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">The world around us has changed in many different ways. We do not physically have to be present in a particular area to experience something new. The virtual world around us is growing day by day and the credit for this goes to all the technological advances that are being observed around us. Because of these technological advancements, almost everything around us has an online version of it, for example, shops and travel agencies. Everything can be done in a matter of a few seconds within a few clicks, and the credit for this convenience goes to the technology around us. The travel industry has also changed tremendously. The biggest change that is observed around us in respect of the travel industry is that the online travel agencies are replacing the traditional travel agencies. One of the biggest advantages of virtual or online travel agencies is that it does not require a lot of initial investment. Starting an online travel agency does however require some sort of financial investment but a lot of money can be saved in many different ways such as investing in a physical workplace or investing in pamphlets and brochures to advertise your travel agency.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">Another unique way that the travel industry has evolved over the years is the way it is advertised and marketed to the world. The traditional ways of advertising include getting brochures and pamphlets printed, and advertising through television ads, TVCs, or through billboards. These ways are very old school and traditional, however, there is one big problem with them that was usually ignored until the modern ways of advertising came about. That problem was them not having a big enough to its targeted audience. This is considered as a very big problem because unless people know about your organization and unless your target audience learns about the benefits that they will be enjoying is they choose your organization over your competitors, you will not be able to generate any demand which automatically means that you will not be able to earn any revenues hence no profits. With the technological advancements observed in the past few decades, the ways through which travel agencies were advertised has also changed drastically.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">The use of social media marketing is being done through different social media platforms such as Facebook, Instagram, and Twitter. Using such social media platforms is a very intelligent way of putting your organization our there in the world. The reason for that is that these days almost every other person has some sort of social media presence so advertising your travel agency would mean that you are reaching out there and communicating your message to a lot more people as compare to reaching and communicating with the masses through traditional advertising styles that have been mentioned above. Different travel agencies in the travel industries have also started reaching out to different bloggers and influencers on these social media platforms because the regular people, who are generally a part of the target audience, tend to trust these bloggers and influencers, and they believe what is said to them through these personalities. Bloggers and influencers are usually paid to post different pictures and stories on their social media platforms that are related to the travel agency. They are also sometimes asked to review the services of the travel agencies once they have been availed or consumed by that particular social media blogger or influencer.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">Another extremely noticeable way through which the travel industry has changed and evolved in the way they function and manage their organizations altogether. Back in the day, when traditional ways were used and implemented by the travel agencies and their affiliated organizations such as airlines and hotels, a lot of time and money was consumed, which could have been used in many other different and more productive ways. Over the past few years, much different software and travel technologies have been developed that are now being used by the travel agencies to improve their efficiency, improve their effectiveness of getting things done, firmly establishing their organization in this extremely competitive world, and earn more profits in the long run.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">Before these technologies and software were developed, the traditional ways involved doing everything manually. Now that everything is automated for the constantly growing world of the travel industries, it is a lot easier to keep track of everything. One of the biggest benefits that travel agencies get to enjoy now is constantly being updated about affiliated organizations. A good example of this could be travel agencies having constant updates about the inventories of the airlines and the hotels along with their rates and charges. Having constant updates about the inventories have greatly helped the travel agencies because it helps them to avoid the problem of overbooking and it also helps them to understand the patterns of consumer demands a little better which will help them in coming up with different pricing strategies according to the consumption and demand patterns of the travelers.</span></span></p>\r\n', '', 1, 1, 0, 'image_750x_5e944a47df690.jpg', 1107, '2020-04-13 07:10:51'),
(132, 1, 'Happy ramdhan 2020', 'happy-ramdhan-2020', '<p>Ramadan is once again amongst us with bundles of Blessings. So, Let&rsquo;s pray to God to bestow politeness in our way of speaking, prosperity in our sources so we can donate more to His individuals. Ramadan Mubarak.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>A little brief about Ramadhan&nbsp;</strong><br />\r\n<br />\r\nRamadan is one of the main holidays for Muslims. This marks the ninth month of the lunar calendar in Islam. This month is thought of as the period of fasting for many Muslims all across the world. In this month, Muslims abstain from real demands, drink, and meals. Whereas Muslims devote themselves repent in their wrongdoings, watch self-sacrifice and spend their attention</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ramadan is a time of spiritual reflection, self-improvement, and heightened devotion and worship. Muslims are expected to put more effort into following the teachings of Islam. The fast (<em>sawm</em>) begins at dawn and ends at sunset. In addition to abstaining from eating and drinking during this time, Muslims abstain from sexual relations<sup><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ramadan#cite_note-AlJazeera-3\">[3]</a></sup>&nbsp;and sinful speech and behaviour. The act of fasting is said to redirect the heart away from worldly activities, its purpose being to&nbsp;<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ritual_purification\" title=\"Ritual purification\">cleanse the soul</a>&nbsp;by freeing it from harmful impurities. Muslims believe that Ramadan teaches them to practice self-discipline, self-control,<sup><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ramadan#cite_note-48\">[47]</a></sup>&nbsp;sacrifice, and empathy for those who are less fortunate, thus encouraging actions of generosity and compulsory charity (<em><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Zakat\" title=\"Zakat\">zakat</a></em>).<sup><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ramadan#cite_note-WP-49\">[48]</a></sup></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Exemptions to fasting include travel, menstruation, severe illness, pregnancy, and breastfeeding. However, many Muslims with medical conditions<sup>[<em><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wikipedia:Vagueness\" title=\"Wikipedia:Vagueness\">vague</a></em>]</sup><sup>[<em><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wikipedia:Manual_of_Style/Words_to_watch#Unsupported_attributions\" title=\"Wikipedia:Manual of Style/Words to watch\">who?</a></em>]</sup>&nbsp;insist on fasting to satisfy their spiritual needs, although it is not recommended by hadith.<sup>[<em><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wikipedia:Citation_needed\" title=\"Wikipedia:Citation needed\">citation needed</a></em>]</sup>&nbsp;Those unable to fast are obligated make up the missed days later.<sup><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ramadan#cite_note-q2-184-50\">[49]</a></sup></p>\r\n\r\n<h4><em>Suhoor</em></h4>\r\n\r\n<p>Main article:&nbsp;<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Suhoor\" title=\"Suhoor\">Suhoor</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Iftar_in_Istanbul_Turkey.jpg\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/b5/Iftar_in_Istanbul_Turkey.jpg/170px-Iftar_in_Istanbul_Turkey.jpg\" style=\"height:227px; width:170px\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Iftar\" title=\"Iftar\">Iftar</a>&nbsp;at&nbsp;<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sultan_Ahmed_Mosque\" title=\"Sultan Ahmed Mosque\">Sultan Ahmed Mosque</a>&nbsp;in&nbsp;<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Istanbul\" title=\"Istanbul\">Istanbul</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Turkey\" title=\"Turkey\">Turkey</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Each day, before dawn, Muslims observe a pre-fast meal called the&nbsp;<em><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Suhoor\" title=\"Suhoor\">suhoor</a></em>. After stopping a short time before dawn, Muslims begin the first prayer of the day,&nbsp;<em><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fajr\" title=\"Fajr\">Fajr</a></em>.<sup><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ramadan#cite_note-51\">[50]</a></sup><sup><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ramadan#cite_note-52\">[51]</a></sup></p>\r\n\r\n<h4><em>Iftar</em></h4>\r\n\r\n<p>Main article:&nbsp;<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Iftar\" title=\"Iftar\">Iftar</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>At sunset, families break the fast with the&nbsp;<em><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Iftar\" title=\"Iftar\">iftar</a></em>, traditionally opening the meal by eating&nbsp;<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Phoenix_dactylifera#Dates\" title=\"Phoenix dactylifera\">dates</a>&nbsp;to commemorate Muhammad&#39;s practice of breaking the fast with three dates.<sup><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ramadan#cite_note-53\">[52]</a></sup><sup><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ramadan#cite_note-54\">[53]</a></sup><sup>[<em><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wikipedia:Citation_needed\" title=\"Wikipedia:Citation needed\">citation needed</a></em>]</sup>&nbsp;They then adjourn for&nbsp;<em><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Maghrib\" title=\"Maghrib\">Maghrib</a></em>, the fourth of the five required daily&nbsp;<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Prayers\" title=\"Prayers\">prayers</a>, after which the main meal is served.<sup><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ramadan#cite_note-55\">[54]</a></sup></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Social gatherings, many times in&nbsp;<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Buffet\" title=\"Buffet\">buffet</a>&nbsp;style, are frequent at&nbsp;<em>iftar</em>. Traditional dishes are often highlighted, including traditional desserts, particularly those made only during Ramadan.<sup>[<em><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wikipedia:AUDIENCE\" title=\"Wikipedia:AUDIENCE\">example needed</a></em>]</sup>&nbsp;Water is usually the beverage of choice, but juice and milk are also often available, as are soft drinks and caffeinated beverages.<sup><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ramadan#cite_note-dieticiannour-56\">[55]</a></sup></p>\r\n\r\n<p>In the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Middle_East\" title=\"Middle East\">Middle East</a>,&nbsp;<em>iftar</em>&nbsp;consists of water, juices, dates, salads and appetizers; one or more main dishes; and rich desserts, with dessert considered the most important aspect of the meal.<sup><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ramadan#cite_note-57\">[56]</a></sup><sup>[<em><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wikipedia:Citation_needed\" title=\"Wikipedia:Citation needed\">citation needed</a></em>]</sup>&nbsp;Typical main dishes include lamb stewed with wheat berries, lamb kebabs with grilled vegetables, and roasted chicken served with chickpea-studded rice pilaf.<sup>[<em><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wikipedia:Citation_needed\" title=\"Wikipedia:Citation needed\">citation needed</a></em>]</sup>&nbsp;Desserts may include&nbsp;<em>luqaimat</em>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Baklava\" title=\"Baklava\">baklava</a>&nbsp;or&nbsp;<em><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kanafeh\" title=\"Kanafeh\">kunafeh</a></em>.<sup><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ramadan#cite_note-la-58\">[57]</a></sup></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Over time, the practice of&nbsp;<em>iftar</em>&nbsp;has involved into banquets that may accommodate hundreds or even thousands of diners.<sup><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ramadan#cite_note-59\">[58]</a></sup>&nbsp;The&nbsp;<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sheikh_Zayed_Grand_Mosque\" title=\"Sheikh Zayed Grand Mosque\">Sheikh Zayed Grand Mosque</a>&nbsp;in&nbsp;<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Abu_Dhabi\" title=\"Abu Dhabi\">Abu Dhabi</a>, the largest mosque in the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/UAE\" title=\"UAE\">UAE</a>, feeds up to thirty thousand people every night.<sup><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ramadan#cite_note-60\">[59]</a></sup>&nbsp;Some twelve thousand people attend&nbsp;<em>iftar</em>&nbsp;at the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Imam_Reza_shrine\" title=\"Imam Reza shrine\">Imam Reza shrine</a>&nbsp;in&nbsp;<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mashhad\" title=\"Mashhad\">Mashhad</a>.<sup><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ramadan#cite_note-61\">[60]</a></sup></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Iftar_Serving_for_fasting_people_in_the_holy_shrine_of_Imam_Reza_05_().jpg\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/a/a9/Iftar_Serving_for_fasting_people_in_the_holy_shrine_of_Imam_Reza_05_%28%29.jpg/220px-Iftar_Serving_for_fasting_people_in_the_holy_shrine_of_Imam_Reza_05_%28%29.jpg\" style=\"height:157px; width:220px\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Iftar serving for fasting people in the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Imam_Reza_shrine\" title=\"Imam Reza shrine\">Imam Reza shrine</a></p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Charity</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Main articles:&nbsp;<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Zak%C4%81t\" title=\"Zakāt\">Zakāt</a>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sadaqah\" title=\"Sadaqah\">Sadaqah</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Men_praying_in_Afghanistan.jpg\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/c/c4/Men_praying_in_Afghanistan.jpg/220px-Men_praying_in_Afghanistan.jpg\" style=\"height:143px; width:220px\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Men praying during Ramadan at the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Shrine_of_Ali\" title=\"Shrine of Ali\">Shrine of Ali</a>&nbsp;or &quot;Blue Mosque&quot; in&nbsp;<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mazar-i-Sharif\" title=\"Mazar-i-Sharif\">Mazar-i-Sharif</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Afghanistan\" title=\"Afghanistan\">Afghanistan</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Zak%C4%81t\" title=\"Zakāt\">Zakāt</a></em>, often translated as &quot;the poor-rate&quot;, is the fixed percentage of income a believer is required to give to the poor; the practice is obligatory as one of the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pillars_of_Islam\" title=\"Pillars of Islam\">pillars of Islam</a>. Muslims believe that good deeds are rewarded more handsomely during Ramadan than at any other time of the year; consequently, many<sup>[<em><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wikipedia:Manual_of_Style/Words_to_watch#Unsupported_attributions\" title=\"Wikipedia:Manual of Style/Words to watch\">who?</a></em>]</sup>&nbsp;donate a larger portion&mdash;or even all&mdash;of their yearly&nbsp;<em>zakāt</em>&nbsp;during this month.<sup>[<em><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wikipedia:Citation_needed\" title=\"Wikipedia:Citation needed\">citation needed</a></em>]</sup></p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Nightly prayers</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Main article:&nbsp;<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tarawih\" title=\"Tarawih\">Tarawih</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tarawih\" title=\"Tarawih\">Tarawih</a></em>&nbsp;(<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Arabic_language\" title=\"Arabic language\">Arabic</a>:&nbsp;تراويح&lrm;) are extra nightly prayers performed during the month of Ramadan. Contrary to popular belief, they are not compulsory.<sup><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ramadan#cite_note-62\">[61]</a></sup></p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Recitation of the Quran</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Muslims are encouraged to read the entire Quran, which comprises thirty&nbsp;<em><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Juz%27\" title=\"Juz\'\">juz&#39;</a></em>&nbsp;(sections), over the thirty days of Ramadan. Some Muslims incorporate a recitation of one&nbsp;<em>juz&#39;</em>&nbsp;into each of the thirty&nbsp;<em><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tarawih\" title=\"Tarawih\">tarawih</a></em>&nbsp;sessions observed during the month.<sup><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ramadan#cite_note-63\">[62]</a></sup></p>\r\n\r\n<p><sup>Credits:&nbsp;</sup><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ramadan\" target=\"_blank\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ramadan</a></p>\r\n', 'happy ramdadhan 2020', 1, 4, 0, 'image_750x_5ea2eb3a4a35a.jpg', 2547, '2020-04-24 13:37:25'),
(133, 1, 'Different ways to startup your online travel portal', 'different-ways-to-startup-your-online-travel-portal', '<p>On the off chance that you are wanting to begin an<a href=\"https://www.phptravels.com\"> <strong>Online Travel Portal</strong></a> effectively read this article cautiously before busy. There are sure factors that should be thought about before beginning an online travel entry.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This is the normal error everyone makes in the process to take their movement business on the web. They don&#39;t break down their prerequisite appropriately. For the most part trip specialists began online business according to their prompt necessity and they bombed over the long haul. Since once they began their entrance they understood that the item they settle or the necessity they choose is insufficient for maintaining their online travel business.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>After settling your necessity you have to choose what sort of item to need to make your movement business on the web. There are numerous modules in Travel Technology and you have to choose which module to need to take.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><u><strong>B2B</strong></u></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Stands for Business to Business this model you will disseminate your items among different organizations and they offer your administrations to the end client. This is the most famous online plan of action among Travel Agents. For the total B2B entrance you will require a spending plan of 5-10 Lacks which incorporates the expense of a few API of providers.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><img src=\"https://lh6.googleusercontent.com/81o03uxEAOHxOJEXR--eqp_lev9dy2uj7aH-a8gG3YC2onvAci4zhd_MDjvfnw7L4PURgRaVccs93UXEIJgbhzJzDtW6HDtSaKpld57SQfKhZX1OfpdC6Le1QGMAwbK38nk3z2_s\" style=\"height:249px; width:624px\" /></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<h2><u><strong>B2C</strong></u></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Stands for Business to Customer. Through this kind of entry, you will ready to arrive at direct client this is the second most famous model among trip specialists. The financial plan required for this sort of Travel Portal is the same as B2B however you should put the great sum in showcasing, SEO, SMO and consume cash in cashback and different offers. The opposition is high in B2B as there are numerous large players in the market and you will require a gigantic spending plan to stand up in the market.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><u><strong>B2E</strong></u></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Stands for Business to Enterprises, is the most up to date model in the Indian travel advertise. Through this kind of movement entry, you will handily move toward large corporate organizations that have an in-house Travel Desk or have an approach where representatives legitimately make his/her set up for Portal. B2E travel entryway is intended for corporate and having office of Employee Profile, Policy Management, Multi-Level Approval System, and some more. Since there are extremely fewer quantities of organizations that give this kind of entryway the expense for building such gateways is exceptionally high and not moderate for a little or medium degree of a trip specialist.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><u><strong>B2B2B</strong></u></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Stands for &quot;Business to Business to Business&quot; it is otherwise called B2B Whitelabel. In this sort of gateway, you are utilizing somebody&#39;s B2B entrance with your area and marking to focus on your B2B specialists. The advancement cost of this kind of entry is less and you can begin this sort of gateway in only 10-20K Rs. Since it isn&#39;t finished B2B entryway you probably won&#39;t gain all the power and usefulness.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><u><strong>B2B2C</strong></u></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Stands for&quot;Business to Business to Customer&quot; it is otherwise called B2C Whitelabel. The main contrast somewhere in the range of B2B2B and B2B2C is through this sort of gateway you can target direct clients rather than Travel Agents.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In the wake of choosing the correct Model or Portal according to your prerequisite, you have to pick<strong><a href=\"https://www.phptravels.com\"> Technology Partner</a> </strong>and this is the most significant advance because for the most part trip specialist has no clue about movement innovation so they effectively trust on innovation supplier and fall into the snare. There is a ton of movement innovation suppliers who professed to be the best in the market however in actuality is they don&#39;t have anything.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'Different ways to startup your online travel portal, tips to start your online travel portal, Different ways to startup your online travel portal in 2020, tip to start online portal in 2020', 1, 1, 0, 'image_750x_5f3a2c1619d89.jpg', 770, '2020-08-17 11:28:44');
